            "title": "鄭嘉穎孖老友黃智賢著「兄弟裝」 年初五現身黃大仙求神",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鄭嘉穎與老友黃智賢在年初五現身黃大仙。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c27be760a0debadcf3a5ec29cfc0416f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250204/_2025020416415735227.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鄭嘉穎與老友黃智賢在年初五現身黃大仙。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>視帝鄭嘉穎與細22年的前港姐冠軍陳凱琳（Grace）2018年結婚，兩人婚後四年抱三，Grace 其後更減少幕前演出，除專注照顧家庭，亦轉型做KOL，做得有聲有色，去年更獲得最吸金KOL排行榜冠軍。鄭嘉穎與Grace 近年密密吸金，商演廣告接不停，日前，就有網民捕獲鄭嘉穎與老友黃智賢在年初五現身黃大仙，祈求新一年事業家庭順利。\n\n</p><h2>兩兄弟齊穿紅衛衣加紅CAP帽</h2>\n<p>網民在社交網分享合照，並開心表示年初五大約下午六時，在黃大仙偶遇鄭嘉穎和黃智賢，相中見鄭嘉穎戴上紅色Cap帽，再配一件紅色衛衣，夠晒意頭，相當搶眼；而黃智賢則滿面鬚根，不過打扮與鄭嘉穎一模一樣，紅帽紅衫，十足「兄弟裝」，平日cool 爆的鄭嘉穎更展現燦爛的笑容與網民合照，似乎心情相當不錯。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃智賢則滿面鬚根與網民合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb5420c52e76a985a0f3a526b3fb0db9/2025-02/01_1_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃智賢則滿面鬚根與網民合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭嘉穎展現燦爛的笑容。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bed2b48e5e3157eb60560895d74dd657/2025-02/02_0_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭嘉穎展現燦爛的笑容。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"二人經常以兄弟裝打扮現身。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/558bda23bf4473ed26577b1f53bc1585/2025-02/394753033_18160870651293739_5272419594352517067_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二人經常以兄弟裝打扮現身。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃智賢更是鄭嘉穎三個兒子的契爺。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/166e1f44cf5599de4b53383ee46aa06a/2025-02/471663043_18476643208012753_810975035057104330_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃智賢更是鄭嘉穎三個兒子的契爺。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"二人一樣很喜歡打網球。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3068be287e13c8d1fffb04abcd4c3556/2025-02/472368633_18479499442015412_7658864581177223569_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二人一樣很喜歡打網球。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄭嘉穎婚後四年抱三，太太Grace其後更減少幕前演出，除專注照顧家庭，亦轉型做KOL。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57d392560cd7306be750108a2ebcb7fe/2025-02/IMG-20250204-WA0029.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄭嘉穎婚後四年抱三，太太Grace其後更減少幕前演出，除專注照顧家庭，亦轉型做KOL。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"二人相識幾十年，非常老友。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bdad079d5e7aad597d88e81231258d4d/2025-02/IMG-20250204-WA0030.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二人相識幾十年，非常老友。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
